main_definition: ( sciences ) An area of land , marked for studying its plants, animals, soil, natural processes, etc.

definitions.definition: A quad ; a blank metal block used to fill space in lines of type .
A virtual rectangular subdivision of a line or column of hieroglyphs within which a group of hieroglyphs is arranged.

main_definition: ( letterpress typography , obsolete ) A quad ; a blank metal block used to fill space in lines of type .
secondary_definitions: ( Egyptology ) A virtual rectangular subdivision of a line or column of hieroglyphs within which a group of hieroglyphs is arranged.
